      // Flag for review, don't auto-remove
      tracing::info!(key, 'Semantic memory not accessed in 90 days');
    }
  }

NOTE: SemanticRecord has ttl: Option<duration> field per types.rs. Check if last_accessed_at exists.

BUILD: cargo build --release
TEST: Create semantic memory with TTL=1s. Wait. Verify removed on next decay tick.
